        }
      ],
      "skos:definition": {
        "@value": "arcus tangent of stem:[x]",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "skos:note": {
        "@value": "stem:[y = \"arctan \"x <=> x = \"tan \"y]\n\n(for stem:[-pi//2 <= y <= pi//2])\n\nThe function stem:[\"arctan\"] is the inverse of the function stem:[\"tan\"] with the restriction mentioned above.\n\nstem:[\"arctg \"x] should not be used.\n",
